Interface ItsNatHTMLTable

All Superinterfaces:
ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatHTMLElementComponent, ItsNatTable, ItsNatUserData
public interface ItsNatHTMLTable
extends ItsNatHTMLElementComponent, ItsNatTable

Is the interface of HTML <table> components.

ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.
